snippet.title: Mickey Storm and the Cursed Mask - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Spy up and save your parents in this action-packed platformer! Can you break the curse on the enchanted waterpark? 🚤

Mickey Storm and the Cursed Mask is a stylized platformer adventure. Available now on PS4 and PS5.
